    - Adjust paths of TFTPROOT and NFSROOT. More properly use our own namespace.
  * conf/debian-edu/fai/debian-edu-fai.TEMPLATE/fai.conf.in:
    - Typo fix.

  * debian/control:
    + Bump Standards-Version: to 4.6.1. No changes needed.
